casebody.head_matter:
James PINKNEY, petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES.
No. 18-6612.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 18, 2019.
On petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit. Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. Judgment vacated, and case remanded to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit for further consideration in light of Stokeling v. United States, 586 U.S. ----, 139 S.Ct. 544, 202 L.Ed.2d 512 (2019).
